{"event": "Built docker exec command args=['docker', 'exec', '--workdir', '/workspace', '--user', '2039:2039', '--env', 'UV_CACHE_DIR=/tmp/uv-cache', '--env', 'PIP_CACHE_DIR=/tmp/pip-cache-dir', '--env', 'PIP_CONFIG_FILE=/tmp/pip-conf', '--env', 'HOME=/tmp/agent_home', '--env', 'ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_SONNET_MODEL=glm-5', '--env', 'ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_OPUS_MODEL=glm-5', '--env', 'ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_HAIKU_MODEL=glm-5', '--env', 'ZHIPU_API_KEY=sk-5tuwV6gfPTdDFv756hMErcAbBzQyVCqZTIZGKWLqgMa1fv72', '--env', 'ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=sk-5tuwV6gfPTdDFv756hMErcAbBzQyVCqZTIZGKWLqgMa1fv72', '--env', 'ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=http://1.95.77.23:3000', '--env', 'FORCE_AUTO_BACKGROUND_TASKS=1', '--env', 'ENABLE_BACKGROUND_TASKS=1', '--env', 'CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_EXPERIMENTAL_BETAS=1', '--env', 'DISABLE_AUTOUPDATER=1', '--env', 'DISABLE_NON_ESSENTIAL_MODEL_CALLS=1', '--env', 'CLAUDE_CODE_DISABLE_NONESSENTIAL_TRAFFIC=1', '4c1922038710c0de97401b20438f4f2cc85fa7c5b175a6cf9c3f51f42ddf48bd', '/bin/sh', '-c', 'claude --output-format stream-json --verbose --model glm-5 --max-turns 100 --permission-mode bypassPermissions --print -- \\'Implement a program that 100% solves the specification. That is all you need to do.\\nKeep using the same virtual environment you started with, update `requirements.txt` with any new dependencies you need.\\nYour task is:\\n## datagate \u2014 Pagination, Sorting, and Response Controls\\n\\n`GET /datasets/<id>` accepts control parameters for pagination, sorting, and shape.\\n\\n### `total`\\n\\nResponses include integer `total` for the row count before pagination.\\n\\n### Pagination\\n\\n`_size` (positive integer, default `100`) limits returned rows. If it exceeds available rows, return all.\\n\\n`_offset` (non-negative integer, default `0`) skips that many rows before returning.\\n\\nInvalid `_size`/`_offset` -> `HTTP 400`.\\n\\n### Sorting\\n\\n`_sort=<column>` sorts ascending by `<column>`.\\n`_sort_desc=<column>` sorts descending by `<column>`.\\n\\nIf both are present, `_sort_desc` wins.\\nSorting is stable and applied before pagination.\\nEmpty values or unknown columns return `HTTP 400`.\\n\\n### Response shape\\n\\n`_shape=lists` (default): `rows` is arrays.\\n\\n`_shape=objects`: `rows` is objects and includes `rowid` (1-based source-file row number). `rowid` is not in `columns`.\\n\\n### Visibility toggles\\n\\n`_rowid=hide` removes `rowid`.\\n`_total=hide` removes `total`.\\nEach toggle is valid only with value `hide`; any other value is `HTTP 400`.\\n\\nAny repeated control parameter (`_size`, `_offset`, `_shape`, `_sort`, `_sort_desc`, `_rowid`, `_total`) is `HTTP 400`.\\n\\n### Error Handling\\n\\n| Condition | HTTP Status | Response |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| `_size` not a positive integer | 400 | `{\"ok\": false, \"error\": \"<message>\"}` |\\n| `_offset` not a non-negative integer | 400 | `{\"ok\": false, \"error\": \"<message>\"}` |\\n| `_shape` not `lists`/`objects` | 400 | `{\"ok\": false, \"error\": \"<message>\"}` |\\n| invalid `_rowid`/`_total` value | 400 | `{\"ok\": false, \"error\": \"<message>\"}` |\\n| control parameter repeated | 400 | `{\"ok\": false, \"error\": \"<message>\"}` |\\n| `_sort`/`_sort_desc` unknown column | 400 | `{\"ok\": false, \"error\": \"<message>\"}` |\\'']", "timestamp": "2026-06-05 01:59:44", "level": "verbose", "process_id": 506223, "thread_name": "MainThread"}
